cs.CR, cs.LG, cs.CV, cs.AI, cs.SE 

The paper deals with detecting attacks on deep neural network image classifiers, which falls under the categories of computer security (cs.CR), machine learning (cs.LG), computer vision (cs.CV), artificial intelligence (cs.AI), and software engineering (cs.SE). However, since the focus is on attacks and defense mechanisms, cs.CR is the most likely category, followed by cs.LG and cs.CV.
